Name: pipeline construction, liquid manure | pipeline, liquid manure | EN15804GD, U
Category: F:Construction/42:Civil engineering/429:Construction of other civil engineering projects/4290:Construction of other civil engineering projects
Description: The pipeworks for liquid manure were modeled, consisting of 20% DN200 and 80% DN100 steel pipelines coated by plastic (polyethylene and polyurethane). Data for construction were based on Frischknecht et al. (1996): Ökoinventare von Energiesystemen: Grundlagen für den ökologischen Vergleich von Energiesystemen und den Einbezug von Energiesystemen in Ökobilanzen für die Schweiz.
Tags: Sector: Infrastructure & Machinery; Agriculture & Animal Husbandry
